{"tid":201602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4月15日之返黎:用2分鐘睇晒各地新聞","createTime":"2017-04-15T01:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T05:56:56.000Z","uid":68591,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c979fec444a729b515d4eda279b8471980780c92","tid":201602,"uid":68591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:22:51.000Z","msg":"早晨! 金仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每條新聞下面既link係新聞既sources,大家想進1步了解既可以入去條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港聞:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 立法會月底將會審議本屆政府最後一份財政預算案，立法會秘書處共接獲745項議員修正案。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170415/s00002/1492192152293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170415%2Fs00002%2F1492192152293&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1ea04e11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170415%2Fs00002%2F1492192152293&h=a7ecaff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170415/s00002/1492192152293</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170415/00176_033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170415%2F00176_033.html&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a1acf128\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170415/00176_033.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 自由黨黨魁鍾國斌透露指建制、泛民政黨負責人5月初將首次設飯局，希望趁新政府上場的契機建立恆常溝通機制。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170415/s00002/1492192148627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170415%2Fs00002%2F1492192148627&d=i3QdlbdnI